| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0224 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 113e3d1b-fc5f-5bb2-8f71-ca35279406a4"
